msgid "What are you looking at?"
msgstr "妳在看什麼？"

msgid "Get out of my face."
msgstr "別出現在我面前。"

msgid "My seat is on the second row from the front, in class 3-C."
msgstr "我的位子在前面數來第二排，3-C 教室。"

msgid "Maybe you don't suck as much as I thought."
msgstr "也許妳沒我想的那麼爛。"

msgid "I'm surprised you even gave it back. Maybe I misjudged you."
msgstr "我很意外妳會還給我。我錯怪妳了。"

msgid "I bet you think you're SO funny. We have other plans for the night anyway."
msgstr "妳一定覺得妳自己很有趣。反正我們今晚還有別的計劃。"

msgid "Whatever you say!"
msgstr "隨便妳怎麼說！"

msgid "Don't talk to me anymore. I won't forget this."
msgstr "別再跟我說話了。我記住妳了。"

msgid "Good luck with your game."
msgstr "祝妳的遊戲順利。"

msgid "(She's really concentrated on fixing her ribbon. Best not to disturb her.)"
msgstr "(她真的很專心地在弄她的緞帶。最好別打擾她。)"

msgid "(She's angrily fidgeting with her ribbon. Best not to bother her anymore.)"
msgstr "(她很生氣地在翻弄她的緞帶。最好別再打擾她了。)"

msgid "It's good to finally make some new friends."
msgstr "能交到新朋友真是太好了。"

msgid "Are you leaving this here?"
msgstr "妳要把這個留下嗎？"

msgid "Why not? I'll pick it up before going home."
msgstr "何不？我回家前再回來拿。"

msgid "May I look through it?"
msgstr "我可以看嗎？"

msgid "No...?"
msgstr "不行...？"

msgid "Ok, let's see..."
msgstr "好，讓我看看..."

msgid "Um... why is there lettuce in your bag?"
msgstr "呃...為什麼妳的書包裡有萵苣？"

msgid "Wha- WHAT DID I JUST SAY!?"
msgstr "妳-妳說什麼！？"

msgid "So... why is there lettuce in your bag?"
msgstr "所以...為什麼妳的書包裡有萵苣？"

msgid "My mom asked me to pick it up on the way home, okay?"
msgstr "我媽要我在回家路上買的，可以嗎？"

msgid "God!"
msgstr "天哪！"

msgid "Fine, fine..."
msgstr "好啦，好啦..."

msgid "You put the lettuce back."
msgstr "把萵苣放回去。"

msgid "It's Saki's bag."
msgstr "這是沙紀的書包。"

msgid "Saki's bag is gone."
msgstr "沙紀的書包不見了。"

msgid "What? Where is my bag?"
msgstr "什麼？我的書包呢？"

msgid "Is someone else here with us?"
msgstr "這裡還有其他人嗎？"

msgid "This isn't good..."
msgstr "不妙..."

msgid "Hopefully it was just the janitor and you can get it back on Monday."
msgstr "希望只是校工，這樣妳星期一就能拿回來了。"

msgid "Uuugh..."
msgstr "呃~~..."

msgid "Isn't this stuffed crow just so cool?"
msgstr "這個填充烏鴉是不是很酷？"

msgid "Oh no."
msgstr "喔不。"

msgid "...So you're that type, huh?"
msgstr "...所以妳是那種人吧？"

msgid "It was an accident! And what is that supposed to mean anyways!?"
msgstr "這只是意外！還有妳這是什麼意思！？"

msgid "It's okay, you can just apologize next week."
msgstr "沒關係，妳可以下星期再道歉。"

msgid "Yeah, it's okay. It was probably the only valuable thing in this room anyways."
msgstr "是啊，沒關係。這大概是這房間裡唯一值錢的東西。"

msgid "Say, what ARE you doing here? Visiting the school at night is hardly normal no matter what you're looking for."
msgstr "是說，妳在這裡做什麼？不管妳在找什麼，在晚上來學校可不正常。"

msgid "I could ask you the same question."
msgstr "我也可以問妳同一個問題。"

msgid "You already know what we were doing."
msgstr "妳已經知道我們剛剛在做什麼了。"

msgid "Key word: \"were\"."
msgstr "關鍵字：\"剛剛\"。"

msgid "Truth is, I'm doing the same thing as you girls... But it's spookier than your game."
msgstr "事實上，我也跟妳們在做一樣的是...只是我的比妳們的遊戲還要更恐怖。"

msgid "A game? Can we join in?"
msgstr "遊戲？我們也可以加入嗎？"

msgid "I thought you had plans for the night?"
msgstr "我以為妳們今晚已經有計劃了？"

msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "We can probably spare an hour or two."
msgstr "我們大概可以分個一兩小時出來。"

msgid "In any case, it's a one-person ritual, so you can't join me on it."
msgstr "無論如何，這是單人儀式，所以妳們不能加入。"

msgid "Figures."
msgstr "早知道。"

msgid "If you like this kind of occult stuff, why aren't you in the club?"
msgstr "如果妳喜歡這種超自然事物，為什麼不加入社團？"

msgid "Only nerds join this club."
msgstr "只有書呆子才加社團。"

msgid "That's not entirely false..."
msgstr "這話有點道理..."

msgid "You didn't bring any other games? Not even a deck of cards?"
msgstr "妳們沒有帶其他遊戲來？連撲克牌都沒有？"

msgid "No, not really."
msgstr "不，沒有。"

msgid "We didn't anticipate someone ruining our game."
msgstr "我們沒想到有人會來破壞我們的遊戲。"

msgid "Fair enough."
msgstr "有道理。"

msgid "So, how did you get in here?"
msgstr "所以，妳們是怎麼進來的？"

msgid "We got a key from someone."
msgstr "我們從某人那邊拿到鑰匙。"

msgid "*I* got a key from someone."
msgstr "*我*從某人那邊拿到鑰匙。"

msgid "...*She* got a key from someone."
msgstr "...*她*從某人那邊拿到鑰匙。"

msgid "Couldn't you just have joined the club?"
msgstr "妳們加入社團不就好了？"

msgid "Why? Is that what you did? Join the club just for the key?"
msgstr "為什麼？妳是這麼做的嗎？只為了拿到鑰匙就加入社團？"

msgid "...This conversation isn't going as planned."
msgstr "...這對話走向跟我想的不一樣。"

msgid "What were you looking for earlier?"
msgstr "妳剛剛在找什麼？"

msgid "Materials for the ritual."
msgstr "儀式用的素材。"

msgid "Shouldn't you have gathered them ahead of time?"
msgstr "妳不是應該預先收集好嗎？"

msgid "Now that's boring. Do you also do your homework ahead of time?"
msgstr "這樣很無聊。妳還會預先寫好功課嗎？"

msgid "I don't know what to say to that."
msgstr "我不知道該怎麼回妳。"

msgid "Will you at least tell us more about your game?"
msgstr "至少告訴我們妳遊戲的內容吧？"

msgid "I'll let you know how it went on Monday."
msgstr "我星期一再告訴妳們結果。"

msgid "If it's anything like the rest I tried, it won't really do anything."
msgstr "如果這跟我其他試過的儀式一樣，那麼會沒什麼用。"

msgid "What's with all the chit chat? Are we suddenly friends or something?"
msgstr "是在閒聊什麼？我們突然變成朋友了還是怎樣？"

msgid "She's alright, I guess."
msgstr "我覺得她還可以。"

msgid "But she ruined our night!"
msgstr "可是她毀了我們的活動！"

msgid "Sorry about that..."
msgstr "對不起..."

msgid "Well... alright, fine."
msgstr "那...好吧，可以。"

msgid "She means \"apology accepted\"."
msgstr "她的意思是\"接受道歉\"。"

msgid "Nice to meet you then, I'm Kat."
msgstr "那麼，很高興認識妳們，我是凱特。"

msgid "We KNOW."
msgstr "我們*知道*。"

msgid "I'm Juli. This is Saki, and this is Kaya."
msgstr "我是由里。她是沙紀。她是香耶。"

msgid "Nice to meet you."
msgstr "很高興認識妳。"

msgid "You know, you're quite the celebrity among third year students."
msgstr "妳知道嗎，妳在三年級中很有名。"

msgid "...for all the wrong reasons."
msgstr "...不是好的那種。"

msgid "You should hang out at 3-C sometime."
msgstr "妳應該來 3-C 晃晃。"

msgid "Do you um... need help with that ribbon?"
msgstr "妳需要，嗯...幫妳弄好緞帶嗎？"

msgid "Ah... no... I'm just fidgeting..."
msgstr "啊...不用...我只是在玩它..."

msgid "Got it."
msgstr "知道了。"

msgid "Don't mind Saki. She's not the bitch she pretends to be."
msgstr "別在意沙紀。她沒有她裝起來的那麼婊。"

msgid "We will probably go home soon."
msgstr "我們大概等等就回家了。"

msgid "Well... at least I got what I needed."
msgstr "好吧...至少我拿到我要的東西了。"

msgid "That's cute!"
msgstr "真可愛！"

msgid "Thank you very much."
msgstr "很感謝妳。"

msgid "Is that supposed to be you...?"
msgstr "這是在畫妳自己嗎...？"

msgid "Please never draw a portrait of me."
msgstr "請不要畫我。"

msgid "Wasn't planning to."
msgstr "沒打算。"

msgid "Kindergarten called, they want their drawing skills back."
msgstr "幼稚園打來了，要妳把他們的繪畫能力還回去。"

msgid "This is my depiction of a child's depiction of a house."
msgstr "這是我對小孩詮釋房子的詮釋。"

msgid "I expected a bit better from you..."
msgstr "我對妳的期望太高了..."

msgid "I didn't."
msgstr "我沒有期望。"

msgid "Draw something on the chalkboard?"
msgstr "在黑板上畫畫？"

msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "What should I draw?"
msgstr "我應該畫什麼？"

msgid "A flower"
msgstr "一朵花"

msgid "A self-portrait"
msgstr "自畫像"

msgid "A house"
msgstr "房子"

msgid "A butt"
msgstr "屁股"

msgid "Don't draw"
msgstr "不要畫"

msgid "It's done!"
msgstr "完成！"

msgid "This was the most pointless thing you've done today."
msgstr "這是妳今天做過最沒有意義的事情。"

msgid "My masterpiece is already perfect, no need for modifications."
msgstr "我的傑作已經很完美了，不需要再做修改。"

msgid "It's too dark for that."
msgstr "這裡太暗了。"

msgid "Say, are any of you members of the theater club?"
msgstr "是說，妳們有人是話劇社員嗎？"

msgid "Not really."
msgstr "不算是。"

msgid "Not really?"
msgstr "不算是？"

msgid "Not me."
msgstr "不是我。"

msgid "Who wants to know?"
msgstr "是誰想知道？"

msgid "Well, there's a talent agent waiting outside. He's only interested in teenage girls with a passion for roleplaying, though."
msgstr "外面有個才藝經紀人在等著。他只對表演有熱忱的青少女有興趣。"

msgid "What is it that you want?"
msgstr "妳要什麼？"

msgid "I just need to borrow something from your club room. You have the key with you, don't you?"
msgstr "我只需要從妳們社辦借個東西。妳有鑰匙，對吧？"

msgid "Hmmm..."
msgstr "嗯~~..."

msgid "Fine, you can have it... If you can do me a favor first."
msgstr "好吧，可以給妳...如果妳先幫我個忙。"

msgid "I'll do you a favor: I'll conveniently forget to tell the principal that you three broke into the school at night. Deal?"
msgstr "我幫妳個忙：我會很巧地忘記告訴校長妳們三個晚上闖進學校，如何？"

msgid "Aren't you trespassing too?"
msgstr "妳就沒有闖進來嗎？"

msgid "So, what's the favor you need?"
msgstr "那麼，妳需要幫什麼忙？"

msgid "Get my notebook. It's in classroom 3-C, under my desk."
msgstr "把我的筆記本拿來。它在 3-C 教室，我的桌子下。"

msgid "Ponytail's Notebook"
msgstr "馬尾女的筆記本"

msgid "A red notebook that the girl with the ponytail forgot. She probably wants it back."
msgstr "一本紅色筆記本，有著馬尾的女孩忘記的。她大概會想要回去。"

msgid "Should I get the notebook for her?"
msgstr "我應該幫她取回筆記本嗎？"

msgid "Alright, I'll do it"
msgstr "好，來吧"

msgid "Forget it"
msgstr "算了"

msgid "You will?"
msgstr "妳要幫忙？"

msgid "Then, when you find it, please don't look through it."
msgstr "那麼，找到的時候，拜託不要讀它。"

msgid "Sure, sure."
msgstr "好，好。"

msgid "Of course, of course."
msgstr "當然，當然。"

msgid "Good luck finding another key to the club room."
msgstr "祝妳順利找到另一把社辦鑰匙。"

msgid "We'll see about that."
msgstr "走著瞧。"

msgid "You mean this one?"
msgstr "妳是說這本嗎？"

msgid "How did you-?"
msgstr "妳是怎麼-？"

msgid "Yes, that's the one."
msgstr "對，就是這本。"

msgid "Here's the key. I expect it back at some point."
msgstr "鑰匙給妳。我期待妳會還給我。"

msgid "Happy to help."
msgstr "樂意之至。"

msgid "Well, you brought my notebook so..."
msgstr "妳把筆記本給我了，所以..."

msgid "Here you go, I guess. Please don't break anything."
msgstr "拿去吧。拜託不要弄壞東西。"

msgid "And don't forget to bring it back to me."
msgstr "還有不要忘記還給我。"

msgid "Thanks!"
msgstr "謝了！"

msgid "There's a bunch of useless trash in here..."
msgstr "一堆沒用的垃圾..."

msgid "Aha! This little box may be it."
msgstr "哈！這小盒子可能就是了。"

msgid "There's three runes... but the ritual didn't mention a specific one."
msgstr "有三顆符石...可是儀式沒有提到要哪一顆。"

msgid "Which one should I take?"
msgstr "我該拿哪一顆？"

msgid "The weird C"
msgstr "奇怪的 C 字"

msgid "The weird B"
msgstr "奇怪的 B 字"

msgid "The weird O"
msgstr "奇怪的 O 字"

msgid "What's that?"
msgstr "那是什麼？"

msgid "A rune. The ritual calls for it."
msgstr "符石。儀式需要它。"

msgid "What does it do?"
msgstr "它有什麼用？"

msgid "No idea."
msgstr "不知道。"

msgid "How is this any less childish than the game we were playing...?"
msgstr "這跟我們的遊戲比起來沒有比較幼稚...？"

msgid "There's a golden envelope in the drawer."
msgstr "抽屜裡有金色的信封。"

msgid "These are the instructions for the ritual I'm doing."
msgstr "這是我要做的儀式的說明。"

msgid "Thankfully, I shortened them when I wrote my notes."
msgstr "慶幸的是，我在寫下筆記時把它縮短了。"

msgid "Read the full ritual rules?"
msgstr "閱讀完整的儀式規則嗎？"

msgid "You must play alone."
msgstr "你必須獨自進行。"

msgid "Requirements:"
msgstr "需求："

msgid ""
"- 3 dark, adjacent rooms\n"
"- 12 candles\n"
"- A lighter or matches"
msgstr ""
"- 3 間黑暗、相連的房間\n"
"- 12 根蠟燭\n"
"- 打火機或是火柴"

msgid ""
"- A rune\n"
"- A tuft of human hair\n"
"- White chalk or white paint"
msgstr ""
"- 一顆符石\n"
"- 一束人髮\n"
"- 白粉筆或是白色顏料"

msgid "Preparations:"
msgstr "準備："

msgid ""
"Start after the sun has set.\n"
"All 3 rooms must be pitch black; turn off all the lights, draw the curtains, and close the doors."
msgstr ""
"在日落後開始。\n"
"3 間房間都必須一片漆黑；關掉所有的燈、關上窗簾、並關上大門。"

msgid "Using the chalk or paint, draw a path going through the 3 rooms. This path will serve to connect your current location to your destination."
msgstr "使用粉筆或是顏料，畫出一條通過 3 個房間的路徑。這條路徑將做為你連接現在地點與目的地的連結。"

msgid "In the middle room, place 6 candles on each side of the drawn path, parallel to it."
msgstr "在中間的房間，放置 6 根蠟燭在路徑兩側，與之平行。"

msgid "Instructions:"
msgstr "說明："

msgid "Light each of the candles and let them burn for at least 5 minutes. From this point, you can no longer abort the ritual."
msgstr "點燃各個蠟燭並讓它們至少燃燒 5 分鐘。從此刻起，你將無法中止儀式。"

msgid ""
"After the 5 minutes have passed, burn the tuft of hair on one of the candles.\n"
"Proceed to blow out all the candles one by one."
msgstr ""
"5 分鐘過後，使用其中一根蠟燭燒掉髮束。\n"
"接著把蠟燭一根一根吹滅。"

msgid "When the last candle is put out, quickly close your eyes and count to 100."
msgstr "當最後一根蠟燭熄滅後，快速閉上眼睛並數到 100。"

msgid "Open your eyes."
msgstr "打開你的眼睛。"

msgid "To Remember:"
msgstr "要記得："

msgid "You must always close the door behind you. Leaving it open may attract unwanted attention."
msgstr "你必須關上你身後的門。避免不必要的注意。"

msgid "Do NOT let the rune out of your possession. It is your only protection."
msgstr "不要讓符石離開你的手邊。它是你唯一的保護。"

msgid "Do NOT bring any weapons with you. If you arm yourself, so will they."
msgstr "不要攜帶任何武器。如果你有武器，祂們也會有。"

msgid "Should anything be heard or felt while you count to 100, it must be ignored."
msgstr "如果有任何事情在你數到 100 之間發生，忽略它。"

msgid "Do NOT open your eyes."
msgstr "不要張開你的眼睛。"

msgid "Do NOT turn on the lights."
msgstr "*不要*開燈。"

msgid "Do NOT move."
msgstr "*不要*移動。"

msgid "It is normal to feel like you are not alone. You won't be."
msgstr "感到不是一個人是很正常的。因為你不是。"

msgid "There's no need to read it again."
msgstr "沒有必要再讀一次。"

msgid "Is that the ritual we're doing right now?"
msgstr "這是我們要做的儀式嗎？"

msgid "Yeah."
msgstr "對。"

msgid "I wonder if anyone else tried it..."
msgstr "不知道有沒有其他人試過..."

msgid "Probably not. It was sealed when I got to it."
msgstr "應該沒有。我拿到的時候它是密封的。"

msgid "That's weird. Did they think it was cursed?"
msgstr "奇怪了。他們覺得這被詛咒了嗎？"

msgid "Maybe. I should probably glue it back later."
msgstr "可能吧。我等等應該把他黏回去。"

msgid "Kat."
msgstr "凱特。"

msgid "Hm?"
msgstr "嗯？"

msgid "Just decide already!"
msgstr "快決定！"

msgid "This window doesn't need any curtains."
msgstr "這扇窗戶不需要任何窗簾。"

msgid "Ugh, you disgust me!"
msgstr "噁，你好噁心！"

msgid "Why are you holding that like some sort of sick trophy? What is wrong with you!?"
msgstr "為什麼你要像是握著獎盃一樣拿著它？你有什麼毛病！？"

msgid "Leave me alone, please."
msgstr "別煩我，拜託。"

msgid "(It's too late to put it back...)"
msgstr "(把它放回去已經太遲了...)"

msgid "Are you done with it?"
msgstr "妳用完了嗎？"

msgid "Yeah, thanks."
msgstr "是啊，謝了。"

msgid "Gee, thanks."
msgstr "唉呀，謝了。"

msgid "(I can't give it back yet, I haven't even used it!)"
msgstr "(我還不能還回去，我根本還沒用它！)"

msgid "...?"
msgstr "...？"

msgid "Uhh... why do you have that?"
msgstr "呃...妳為什麼拿著它？"

msgid "Well, thanks for returning it, I guess?"
msgstr "好吧，謝謝妳的歸還...囉？"

msgid "Let me guess. Returning my notebook was too much for you, so you just took the key instead."
msgstr "讓我猜猜。把我的筆記本拿給我太麻煩了，所以妳就直接拿走鑰匙。"

msgid "Well, at least you brought it back, I suppose."
msgstr "好吧，至少妳把它拿回來了。"

msgid "Oh wow. You just took that?"
msgstr "喔哇。妳就直接把它拿走了？"

msgid "You're a real bitch Kat, you know that?"
msgstr "妳真的很討人厭凱特，妳知道嗎？"

msgid "...of course you had it all along."
msgstr "...當然了，妳一直拿著它。"

msgid "Now I feel like an idiot for worrying. Hope you enjoyed my key."
msgstr "現在我覺得像笨蛋一樣白擔心了。享受我的鑰匙吧。"

msgid "That won't accomplish anything good."
msgstr "這樣不會有什麼好後果。"

msgid "(I feel like setting her on fire but... I'll control myself.)"
msgstr "(我好想在她身上放火...我得控制我自己)"

msgid "What?"
msgstr "什麼？"

msgid "(She really isn't that bad.)"
msgstr "(她真的沒那麼糟糕。)"

msgid "(It would be a shame to set such pretty hair on fire.)"
msgstr "(把這麼漂亮的頭髮燒了會很可惜。)"

msgid "(Nah...)"
msgstr "(還是不要...)"

msgid "Is this your notebook?"
msgstr "這是妳的筆記本嗎？"

msgid "Yeah, that's it. I hope you didn't look through it."
msgstr "是啊，沒錯。我希望妳沒有看過它。"

msgid "Nope. Your secrets are safe."
msgstr "沒有。妳的秘密很安全。"

msgid "Alright."
msgstr "好吧。"

msgid "Nope. Your math is safe."
msgstr "沒有。妳的數學很安全。"

msgid "Of course you looked. Hope you at least solved some of the exercises."
msgstr "妳果然看過了。希望妳至少解了一些題目。"

msgid "What? Did you really think I'd leave my personal journal in your hands?"
msgstr "什麼？妳真的以為我會把我的日記交到妳手上嗎？"

msgid "Well, a promise is a promise anyways."
msgstr "好吧，說到做到。"

msgid "Here's the key. Bring it back when you're done with it."
msgstr "鑰匙拿去。用完了要還給我。"

msgid "Yeah, that's it. But, you don't need the key anymore, do you?"
msgstr "對，就是這個。但是，妳不需要鑰匙了吧？"

msgid "Why did you bother stealing it if you were gonna get me the notebook either way?"
msgstr "既然妳要給我筆記本為什麼還要偷它？"

msgid "Sigh... whatever. Thanks, weirdo."
msgstr "唉...隨便吧。謝了，怪胎。"

msgid "*gasp*"
msgstr "*抽氣*"

msgid "I uh... I don't seem to have the key with me."
msgstr "我呃...我身上沒有鑰匙。"

msgid "I could've sworn I had it... I'm sorry. I promise to let you use it tomorrow!"
msgstr "我記得我有啊...對不起。我明天一定會讓妳用它！"

msgid "It's fine! Don't worry about it!"
msgstr "沒關係！別放在心上！"

msgid "Do you seriously think I'll give you the key after what you did?"
msgstr "妳真的覺得妳幹出這事後我會給妳鑰匙嗎？"

msgid "...Yes?"
msgstr "...會？"

msgid "Piss off, Kat. And give me that!"
msgstr "快滾，凱特。還有把它給我！"

msgid "You don't even care? Whatever. Give me that!"
msgstr "妳根本就不在乎？隨便。把它給我！"

msgid "You come here, you ruin our game, you cut our hair, you steal my things and now you just bring me this?"
msgstr "妳到這裡，妳毀了我們的遊戲，妳剪掉我們的頭髮，妳偷了我的東西，然後現在妳把這個給我？"

msgid "I have no words left for you, you little sociopath."
msgstr "我無話可說了，妳這神經病。"

msgid "Does this happen to be yours?"
msgstr "這是妳的嗎？"

msgid "Huh? Why do you have that? Are you going through my stuff now?"
msgstr "蛤？妳為什麼拿著它？妳在翻我的東西嗎？"

msgid "Nah... I just had a feeling."
msgstr "沒有...只是我的直覺。"

msgid "Your feeling is right. May I have my notebook back?"
msgstr "妳的直覺是對的。我可以拿回我的筆記本嗎？"

msgid "Here you go."
msgstr "拿去吧。"

msgid "Are you kidding me? First the hair and now blackmail?"
msgstr "開什麼玩笑？一開始是頭髮然後是勒索？"

msgid "I don't care what you want, and I don't care why you have my notebook."
msgstr "我才不管妳想要什麼，我也不想知道妳為什麼有我的筆記本。"

msgid "Give it back or I'll get the teacher to beat your ass tomorrow morning!"
msgstr "把它還來不然明天早上找老師來教訓妳！"

msgid "Geez... Stuff it. I don't want your stupid notebook."
msgstr "唉呀...算了。我不想要妳的蠢筆記本。"

msgid "Hey, is this yours?"
msgstr "嘿，這是妳的嗎？"

msgid "Um..."
msgstr "嗯..."

msgid "Wait, can I see that...?"
msgstr "等等，我可以看看嗎...？"

msgid "For the love of... give me that!"
msgstr "妳是在...把它給我！"

msgid "What are you doing...? Please bring that here."
msgstr "妳在做什麼...？請把它拿過來。"

msgid "Uhh..."
msgstr "呃..."

msgid "For the love of... bring that here!"
msgstr "妳是在...把它給我！"

msgid "Finally, let's cut this open."
msgstr "終於，把它割開吧。"

msgid "(Nothing else needs cutting here.)"
msgstr "(沒有東西需要被割開了。)"

msgid "...!"
msgstr "...！"

msgid "Did you just...?"
msgstr "妳剛剛...？"

msgid "Oh. My. God."
msgstr "我。的。天。哪。"

msgid "WHAT HAVE YOU DONE!?"
msgstr "妳做了什麼！？"

msgid "GET THE HELL OUT!!!"
msgstr "快滾開！！！"

msgid "Get away from me!"
msgstr "離我遠一點！"

msgid "(I already got all the hair I need, no need to be petty.)"
msgstr "(我已經拿到我需要的頭髮了，不需要這麼小氣。)"

msgid "(Nah... she's fine.)"
msgstr "(算了...她是好人。)"

msgid "...!?"
msgstr "...！？"

msgid "What in the actual hell..."
msgstr "妳到底是在..."

msgid "Are you kidding me right now!?"
msgstr "開什麼玩笑！？"

msgid "Oh no..."
msgstr "喔不..."

msgid "DON'T TOUCH HER! GET OUT OF HERE!"
msgstr "別碰她！快滾！"

msgid "Don't you dare..."
msgstr "妳最好不要..."

msgid "(I don't need to do that. Plus, I kinda like her hair - it's a pretty color.)"
msgstr "(我不需要那麼做。而且，我還滿喜歡她的頭髮的-顏色很漂亮。)"

msgid "(I don't wanna ruin her hair.)"
msgstr "(我不想毀了她的頭髮。)"

msgid "WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU DOING TO HER!?"
msgstr "妳對她做了什麼！？"

msgid "She cut... her hair..."
msgstr "她剪了...她的頭髮..."

msgid "Why...?"
msgstr "為什麼...？"

msgid "GET OUT RIGHT THIS SECOND!!!"
msgstr "現在馬上滾開！！！"

msgid "Kat, if you touch me with those scissors..."
msgstr "凱特，如果妳對我用了那把剪刀..."

msgid "I'll make you swallow them."
msgstr "我會讓妳吞了它。"

msgid "(She looks like she's asking for it, but I already have all the hair I need.)"
msgstr "(她看起來像是自找麻煩，但是我已經有了需要的頭髮了。)"

msgid "(She doesn't deserve it, I think.)"
msgstr "(她不該受這罪，我想是吧。)"

msgid "It's a school bag."
msgstr "是書包。"

msgid "There's something shiny inside."
msgstr "裡面有亮亮的東西。"

msgid "Do you need something?"
msgstr "你需要什麼嗎？"

msgid "Maybe later."
msgstr "等等吧。"

msgid "(What if I accidentally push the bag off the chair?)"
msgstr "(如果我不小心把書包推下椅子呢？)"

msgid "Push the bag?"
msgstr "推書包？"

msgid "What the-!"
msgstr "什麼-！"

msgid "I'm so sorry! Oh dear me, let me pick that up for you!"
msgstr "我很抱歉！看我笨手笨腳的，讓我幫妳把它撿起來！"

msgid "I'll be out of your hair now!"
msgstr "我不會再煩你了！"

msgid "(No need to mess with it anymore.)"
msgstr "(不需要再亂搞它了。)"

msgid "An empty chair with no bag on it."
msgstr "沒有書包的空椅子。"

msgid "An empty chair."
msgstr "空椅子。"

msgid "It's the box for the game the girls were playing."
msgstr "這是女孩們剛剛在玩的遊戲的盒子。"

msgid "It says \"Wiji Game Board - for 2 to 4 players. Get answers from beyond!\"."
msgstr "上面寫著\"通靈遊戲盤 - 2 至 4 人。得到來自另一個世界的答案！\"。"

msgid "\"WARNING: We take no responsibility for any adverse effects playing this game could cause to you or your loved ones.\""
msgstr "\"警告：我們不為任何遊戲對您或您親人造成的不良影響負責。\""

msgid "Such as disappointment, I presume?"
msgstr "真讓我失望？"

msgid "The disappointment was your fault, though..."
msgstr "是妳讓我們很失望的欸..."

msgid "A thick purple book."
msgstr "厚重的紫色書本。"

msgid "(A spellbook? It looks weird. And it also looks fake.)"
msgstr "(魔法書？看起來很奇怪。而且還看起來很假。)"

msgid "There's a book entitled \"Creepy Cryptids and where to find them\"."
msgstr "其中一本的標題是\"詭異生物與牠們的產地\"。"

msgid "There's a book entitled \"The truth behind mermaids exposed\"."
msgstr "其中一本的標題是\"美人魚的真相曝光\"。"

msgid "There's a book entitled \"Magic Circles for simpletons\"."
msgstr "其中一本的標題是\"傻瓜也能懂的魔法陣\"。"

msgid "Cardboard boxes marked with a symbol. They're sealed with tape."
msgstr "印著標誌的紙盒。它被膠帶封起來了。"

msgid "(The runes my friend mentioned may be in here, but I need a way to open it.)"
msgstr "(我朋友提到的符石可能就在裡面，可是我需要想辦法打開它。)"

msgid "(I need a way to open this, I'm not going to carry the entire box around.)"
msgstr "(得想辦法打開它，我不想帶著箱子到處跑。)"

msgid "(There are two runes left in the box, but I only need one for the ritual.)"
msgstr "(箱子裡還剩兩顆符石，可是我只需要一顆來完成儀式。)"

msgid "(But maybe I picked the wrong one...)"
msgstr "(可是我可能選錯顆了...)"

msgid "Switch my rune"
msgstr "換掉符石"

msgid "Do nothing"
msgstr "什麼也不做"

msgid "Which one then?"
msgstr "那要選哪顆呢？"

msgid "Just take everything"
msgstr "全部拿走好了"

msgid "Well, it doesn't say I CAN'T have more than one."
msgstr "其實，也沒有說我不能多拿幾個。"

msgid "If only there were four..."
msgstr "如果有四顆的話..."

msgid "We could get one each. Not that they do anything."
msgstr "我們就可以一人拿一顆。不過大概也沒什麼用。"

msgid "There's nothing else of use."
msgstr "沒有什麼有用的東西了。"

msgid "I need to get this open..."
msgstr "我需要打開它..."

msgid "Um... ever heard of nails?"
msgstr "嗯...妳知道什麼是指甲嗎？"

msgid "Well..."
msgstr "那麼..."

msgid "Ugh, step aside."
msgstr "吼，讓我來。"

msgid "Tada!"
msgstr "看吧！"

msgid "Saki is so practical..."
msgstr "沙紀真是行動派的..."

msgid "Man... is this your idea of fun?"
msgstr "唉呀...這是妳們取樂的方法嗎？"

msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr "什麼意思？"

msgid "It doesn't matter. Now let's see..."
msgstr "算了。來看看吧..."

msgid "A clean chalkboard."
msgstr "乾淨的黑板。"

msgid "My fabulous masterpiece is displayed here."
msgstr "我的大師傑作展示於此。"

msgid "There's some chalk here."
msgstr "這裡有一些粉筆。"

msgid "Take Chalk?"
msgstr "拿走粉筆？"

msgid "But it's too dark to see now."
msgstr "可是這裡太暗了。"

msgid "A stuffed crow."
msgstr "填充烏鴉。"

msgid "(An interesting choice of decoration...)"
msgstr "(用來當裝飾還真特別...)"

msgid "It's messed up now."
msgstr "已經被弄壞了。"

msgid "A crystal ball resting on a cushion."
msgstr "在墊子上的水晶球。"

msgid "(Wow, that cheap plastic exterior really makes it look authentic.)"
msgstr "(哇，這塑膠外殼看起來就像真的一樣。)"

msgid "This drawer won't open."
msgstr "這個抽屜打不開。"

msgid "(I don't see a keyhole, so it must be stuck somehow.)"
msgstr "(我找不到鑰匙孔，所以一定是被卡住了。)"

msgid "There's nothing of use here."
msgstr "沒有什麼有用的東西了。"

msgid "Don't even bother sitting with us after you ruined our night."
msgstr "毀了我們的夜晚還想坐在旁邊啊。"

msgid "Can't you read the room? We don't want you around. Leave!"
msgstr "會不會看氣氛啊？我們不想看到妳。走開！"

msgid "An empty chair. Sit down?"
msgstr "空椅子。坐下嗎？"

msgid "The girls are gone."
msgstr "女孩們離開了。"

msgid "A spherical model of the Earth. Red crosses mark certain locations."
msgstr "圓球狀的地球模型。紅色的叉叉標記了一些地點。"

msgid "Some books and jars filled with.... something."
msgstr "一些書本和罐子，裡面裝著....某種東西。"

msgid "There's no need to mess with the lights anymore."
msgstr "不需要再動電燈開關了。"

msgid "The light switch isn't working."
msgstr "電燈開關沒有作用。"

msgid "Some small plants. Their quiet existence fascinates you."
msgstr "小植物。他們寂靜的存在令我著迷。"

msgid "The drawer underneath is empty."
msgstr "抽屜是空的。"

msgid "Suspicious news articles and posters representing magic circles."
msgstr "可疑的新聞報導和有著魔法陣的海報。"

msgid "An expensive-looking radio."
msgstr "看起來很貴的收音機。"

msgid "Turn it on?"
msgstr "開啟它嗎？"

msgid "What are you even doing?"
msgstr "妳到底在做什麼？"

msgid "Just looking around."
msgstr "只是看看。"

msgid "No need to turn it on again."
msgstr "不需要再開啟它了。"

msgid "It has no power."
msgstr "它沒電了。"

msgid "A trash can. It seems to be full."
msgstr "垃圾桶。看起來滿了。"

msgid "There's a certain level of desperation needed for someone to dig through the trash. You're not at that level."
msgstr "翻遍垃圾需要有著某種程度的決心。妳還沒到那個程度。"

msgid "A cool breeze blows in from outside."
msgstr "涼風從外面吹來。"

msgid "Close the window?"
msgstr "關上窗戶？"

msgid "Open the window?"
msgstr "打開窗戶？"

msgid "...Huh?"
msgstr "...咦？"

msgid "I can't seem to open it..."
msgstr "好像打不開..."

msgid "Are you trying to freak us out on purpose?"
msgstr "妳是在嚇我們？"

msgid "(These curtains are very thin. I don't think they would work.)"
msgstr "(那些簾布太薄了。我不認為有用。)"

msgid "(Better read my notes to make sure I'm not forgetting anything in this room before leaving.)"
msgstr "(最好在離開前再讀一次我的筆記以免忘了什麼東西。)"
